# Honored by the repo-root build context (context: ../..) for -f apps/dashboard/Dockerfile.
# A plain apps/dashboard/.dockerignore is IGNORED with a root context; this name is the
# Dockerfile-scoped ignore Docker/BuildKit reads. Globs (**/) are required because
# context-root-relative bare `node_modules` would only match /node_modules, not the
# nested workspace copies.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
